snippet.title: Mrs.Cat in Mars - PC Gameplay (Steam)
snippet.description:
[The video file for this tiny game is 19.1 gigabytes, by the way. Think about it for a second...]

Help Mrs.Cat to complete a mission: Explore Mars and collect the energy gems.In this 2d precision platformer, you'll have to memorize and face the invisible and visible deadly objects, running, jumping and meowing!

Mrs.Cat in Mars (C) EVEV01
